title: MSNBC Admits They Control What You Think
text:
MSNBC Admits They Control What You Think Freudian slip reveals the media's attitude toward the American public Joe Biggs | Infowars.com - February 23, 2017 Comments 
Infowars reporter Joe Biggs breaks down a new clip from MSNBC’s Mika Brzezinski who admits that it’s the mainstream media’s job to tell the American people what to think and claims President Trump needs to basically stop bypassing them so they can tell you what’s fake and what isn’t.
